column2: Residential Building Permits (Number of single dwelling units)

column1: Adapted from Statistics Canada, Building Permits (BPER), March 2025. This does not constitute an endorsement by Statistics Canada of this product.
Latest month is preliminary, month previous to latest month is revised.
RDR = Regional District Remainder, all reporting areas not otherwise listed.
SGC codes ending in 000 refer to the regional district remainder, and may be the sum of multiple census subdivisions.
*Fort Nelson was amalgamated with Northen Rockes RM in Feb 2009
** Area amalgamated into Regional District Remainder (RDR) for the regional district as of June 2009
***Regional district abolished in 2008, replaced by Comox Valley RD and Strathcona RD
**** Refers to Salt Spring Island RDA from 2016 onwards and to the Capital RDR prior to 2016.
